l, “Injuries and Overuse Syndromes in Powerlifting,” International Journal of Sports Medicine 32, no. 9 (2011), 703-711.</li><li>James L. Nuzzo, “Sex Difference in Participation in Muscle-Strengthening Activities,” Journal of Lifestyle Medicine 10, no. 2 (2020): 110-115.</li><li>Joseph J. Crisco, James C. Coburn, Douglas C. Moore, Mohammad A. Upal, “Carpal Bone Size and Scaling in Men versus in Women,” Journal of Hand Surgery (American) 30, no. 1 (2005): 35-42.</li><li>Kevin M. Trahey, Evan M. Lapp, Trent N. Talipan, Thomas J. Guydan, Alexander J. Krupka, Carrie E. Ellis, “The Effect of Lifting Straps on Deadlift Performance in Females,” Journal of Strength and Conditioning Research 37, no. 10  (2023): 1924-1928.</li><li>Seyed Saeed Tamehri Zadeh, Seyyed Saeed Moazzeni, Samaneh Asgari, Mohammadhassan Mirbolouk, Fereidoun Azizi, Farzad Hadaegh, “Association between Wrist Circumference and Risk of Any Fracture in Adults: Findings from 15 Years of Follow-Up in the Tehran Lipid and Glucose Study,” Journal of Clinical Medicine 11, no. 23 (2022):  7048.</li><li>All photos are made by our WBCM Media team.</li></ol>",
